idc = idb.IDAPython(kernel32_idb).idc
flags = idc.GetFlags(1754271760)
assert idc.hasValue(flags) is True
byte = idc.IdbByte(1754271760)
assert byte == 139
with pytest.raises(KeyError):
    idc.GetFlags(2290649224)
    assert idc.hasValue(idc.GetFlags(2290649224)) is True
assert idc.ItemSize(1754271760) == 2
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    idc.ItemSize(1754271761)
assert idc.ItemSize(1754271762) == 1
assert idc.GetManyBytes(1754271760, 3) == b'\x8b\xffU'
kern32_test()
